              "options": {
                "content": "### Your Project Workbook\n\nThis board is a **live picture of your project's setup** \u2014 the handful of foundational decisions the build needs before it can create your app. Each row is one **input**; the colored marker shows where it stands. Nothing here is final and you can't break anything \u2014 the board just reflects what's on disk. Use the **audience** selector at the top to switch how much detail you see. Start with the \ud83d\udd34 gaps.",
                "mode": "markdown"
              }
            }
          }
        }
