              "options": {
                "content": "The **Digital Project Workbook** \u2014 the shared, whole-project view of the foundational kickoff decisions. A dynamic, query-based evolution of Brooks' workbook (_The Mythical Man-Month_), which was static (paper/microfiche); this one is generated from live project state. Flip the **audience** variable (top of the board) to switch persona in-browser \u2014 no regeneration, no write.",
                "mode": "markdown"
              }
            }
